data.description:
Beautiful Two Story Prairie Waters Home on 2 Acres! Huge great room with stone fireplace open to the kitchen with a massive island and granite countertops. The master suite of this 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bath home is a must see! The double door walk in closet and double door bathroom are fabulous. Enjoy the catwalk upstairs to the other 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.
Home is being sold as is. Seller will provide First American Home Warranty Max Plan.
